  "detailed_description": "Guide your сar avatar through the world made of tiles. Uncover hidden paths, meet friends and outsmart enemies. Each level of the game is a unique tiny adventure.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/356170/extras/9f95c9ed74fdd7f96c94e739a7f174b5.avif?t=1447963022\" width=405 height=178 /></span><br>The player controls the car, which can be equipped with a weapon and a magnet gadget that can move objects.<br>In most cases levels can be completed with smart logical solutions, but sometimes the player has to enter battles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/356170/extras/002b9dd70a9a0ccc827c3ad7d042562f.avif?t=1447963022\" width=316 height=194 /></span>",
